      "text": [
        " : «اَلْبَقَرَةُ وَ اَلْبَدَنَةُ تُجْزِيَانِ عَنْ سَبْعَةِ نَفَرٍ إِذَا كَانُوا مِنْ أَهْلِ بَيْتٍ أَوْ مِنْ غَيْرِهِمْ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3052 - Wuhayb ibn Hafs narrated from Abu Abdullah (as) who said:\n\"A cow or a camel suffices for seven individuals, whether they are from one household or from different ones.\""
